data.revised_prompt: Create a photorealistic, high-quality image of a 'Tequila Verde Smash' cocktail. The drink should be presented in a transparent, stylish rocks glass and exhibit a refreshing light green tone. The glass should house aesthetically placed cucumber slices and feature three pristine basil leaves floating on the surface. There should be a thin slice of lime elegantly garnishing the rim of the glass. Light should stream in from the left, casting gentle reflections and highlights that accentuate the vibrant color of the drink. The backdrop of the image should be a blurred wooden texture, promoting a fresh and organic ambience. The image composition should underscore elegance and freshness through its minimalistic aesthetic. The cocktail ingredients should not be listed in the image, and there should be no text or watermarks present. The background should be clear with a soft focus, mimicking the style of a professional food photograph.
